\begin{frame}{\textcolor{red}{Anomalies}}
\begin{block}{Regions}
\begin{itemize}

\item Can select a region eg Southern Oscillation, ENSO 3.4 and run off anomalies
\item kCARTA jacobians .. about 1 day
\item Unlike AMT 2020 paper, here I just used same jacobian at each time step .. but allowed CO2/N2O/CH4/CFC to ramp
\item Takes a couple so hours to process eg +/- 10 lat and then about an hour to read in 500 tiles x 412 time steps!
\item \textcolor{blue}{TESTS - can examine radiance anomaly spectral residuals}
\item \textcolor{blue}{TESTS - anomaly retrievals can be compared to geophysical anomalies, as can trends}
\item \textcolor{red}{CLOSURE TESTS - generate BT anomalies from retrieved geophysical anomalies, \emph{compare to observed BT anomalies}}
\end{itemize}
\end{block}

\end{frame}

